subject: Preparation for Q4 Pitch Day
snippet: Marcus congratulates Adam on being selected for Q4 Pitch Day and requests his updated deck...
body_plain:
Adam,

Congratulations on being selected to present at our Q4 Pitch Day event!

Event Details:
üìÖ Thursday, November 13, 2025
‚è∞ 1:00-2:00 PM EST
üîó Zoom (link will be sent separately)

Next Steps:

subject: Re: Carlo Acutis Cohort
snippet: Robert proposes new meeting time slots and asks everyone to share their availability...
body_plain:
Hi everyone,

Thanks for your patience as we work to find a new meeting time that works for the whole cohort.

Based on the feedback so far, here are the proposed time slots (all in Central Time):
- Monday 3:00 PM CT
- Tuesday 3:00 PM CT
- Wednesday 3:00 PM CT
- Wednesday 8:00 AM CT

Please reply to this email with any times that DON'T work for you, and I'll select the best option once I hear from everyone.

For context, we want to maintain our weekly fellowship meetings while ensuring maximum participation.

Blessings,
Robert Kim
Carlo Acutis Fellowship Coordinator

subject: Re: Carlo Acutis Cohort
snippet: David confirms that 8am CT doesn't work for his schedule...
body_plain:

The 8am CT slot doesn't work for me unfortunately.

The afternoon options should be fine though.

Thanks,
David
